<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Mystic-Type</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Multiplayer<sp/>R-Type-like<sp/>with<sp/>an<sp/>authoritative<sp/>TCP/UDP<sp/>server<sp/>and<sp/>a<sp/>raylib<sp/>graphical<sp/>client.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
