<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>C++17<sp/>compiler</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>raylib<sp/>(fetched<sp/>automatically<sp/>via<sp/>FetchContent)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Works<sp/>on<sp/>macOS,<sp/>Linux,<sp/>and<sp/>Windows<sp/>(WSA<sp/>init<sp/>handled<sp/>in<sp/>entry<sp/>points).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
